    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. This example delivers a linear power curve with a sharp 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a factory limited-slip differential and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. Recent maintenance includes a subframe inspection and cooling system refresh to ensure sustained performance under load. With dialed-in suspension kinematics and robust compression across all cylinders, this M3 offers an authentic, driver-centric experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
