      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a refined driving experience and a complete history of care. The exterior finish retains a deep, impressive gloss, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch, typical of a well-loved daily driver. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership; the leather seating is supple and free of cracks, and every button, dial, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced exclusively with synthetic oil. Recent maintenance includes a fresh brake pad replacement and a new set of all-season tires with approximately 85% tread remaining. The car has been kept in a smoke-free and pet-free environment, and it comes with a complete binder of service records, the original owner's manuals, and two programmed key fobs. This is a turnkey opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality vehicle without the new-car price tag.",
